name: ps2ff
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.5.2" %}

package:
  name: ps2ff
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/usgs/ps2ff/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f6cfd4593b48e0e16b0bcfc5ffc51c0a98c509d10f3045004b3fe88f5993b7f2

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - numpy
    - scipy
    - pandas
    - configobj

test:

  imports:
    - ps2ff

about:
  home: https://github.com/usgs/ps2ff
  license: Public Domain
  summary: 'Produce approximated earthquake rupture distances from point source information.'
  license_family: Public Domain
  license_file: LICENSE.md

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mhearne-usgs
    - emthompson-usgs
    - cbworden
